episodes.overview: Sandy creates an acorn food sensation, but her tree pays the price for her greed.

episodes.name: Food Con Castaways
episodes.overview: The gang heads to a food convention, but things go awry when they get lost in the woods.

episodes.name: Pineapple Invasion
episodes.overview: In this episode, SpongeBob hides the Krabby Patty secret formula in his home, and Gary must protect it from Plankton.

episodes.name: Salsa Imbecilicus
episodes.overview: Sandy must save the day, after everyone in town becomes as stupid as Patrick.

episodes.name: Bulletin Board
episodes.overview: SpongeBob puts up a community bulletin board but anonymous reviews lead to trouble.

episodes.name: Mutiny on the Krusty
episodes.overview: When a storm blows away the Krusty Krab, an insane Mr. Krabs has to guide his employees and customers back to their homes.

episodes.name: Whirlybrains
episodes.overview: SpongeBob and Patrick get hooked on the latest fad – flying your own brain like a tiny drone.

episodes.name: Snail Mail
episodes.overview: SpongeBob lies to his penpal and continues the foul play when he visits.

episodes.name: MermaidPants
episodes.overview: SpongeBob and Patrick have fun playing Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy, and Mr. Krabs and Squidward decide to play along as the bad guys.

episodes.name: The Whole Tooth
episodes.overview: Patrick has to lose his last baby tooth, but he is frightened.

episodes.name: Goodbye, Krabby Patty?
episodes.overview: SpongeBob and Mr. Krabs seek business advice from an ad executive in Mr. Krabs’ endeavor to launch a line of frozen Krabby Patties.

episodes.name: Mimic Madness
episodes.overview: SpongeBob learns that imitation is the sincerest form of flattery.

episodes.name: House Worming
episodes.overview: When worms move in to SpongeBob's holes, it's up to him to hide his disgusting new friends from everyone else.

episodes.name: Snooze You Lose
episodes.overview: Squidward is so tired that SpongeBob and Patrick cannot wake him up, but they will not let him miss his big audition.

episodes.name: Krusty Katering
episodes.overview: Mr. Krabs and his crew cater a fancy party, but they might be out of their depth with their new wealthy customers

episodes.name: SpongeBob's Place
episodes.overview: SpongeBob cooks at home, prompting Mr. Krabs' customers to leave his restaurant and head for SpongeBob's place.

episodes.name: Plankton Gets the Boot
episodes.overview: Karen does not want Plankton to stay at the Chum Bucket anymore, leaving it up to SpongeBob to teach Plankton how to make it up to her.

episodes.name: Life Insurance
episodes.overview: A misunderstanding leads SpongeBob and Patrick to try to prove their life insurance protects them from any danger.

episodes.name: Burst Your Bubble
episodes.overview: Mrs. Puff is not pleased when SpongeBob blows himself a bubble boat.

episodes.name: Plankton Retires
episodes.overview: Plankton decides to close the Chum Bucket and move to a new town, but Mr. Krabs still suspects he is up to something.

episodes.name: Trident Trouble
episodes.overview: SpongeBob accidentally picks up King Neptune's magic trident.

episodes.name: Unreal Estate
episodes.overview: SpongeBob fears that he is allergic to his pineapple house and Squidward offers to help him find a new home and trouble ensues.

episodes.name: Code Yellow
episodes.overview: Squidward plans to get a nose job at the hospital and SpongeBob decides to tag along.

episodes.name: The Getaway
episodes.overview: When SpongeBob mistakes an escaped convict for his driving instructor, it’s the new teacher who learns a lesson.

episodes.name: Lost and Found
episodes.overview: Mr. Krabs sends SpongeBob in search of a missing toy, and SpongeBob finds himself lost in the lost-and-found.

episodes.name: Patrick's Coupon
episodes.overview: Patrick has a coupon for free ice cream, but if he wants to use it, he has to enter the store.

episodes.name: Out of the Picture
episodes.overview: Mr. Krabs buys Squidward's art, but he has to get the artist out of the picture to make profit.

episodes.name: Spot Returns
episodes.overview: When his pet amoeba Spot has puppies, Plankton decides to use them in another of his nefarious plots.

episodes.name: The Check-Up
episodes.overview: Mr. Krabs is afraid to get his physical, but if he does not pass the Krusty Krab will be shut down.

episodes.name: Sportz?
episodes.overview: Squidward invents a new sport to get back at SpongeBob and Patrick for annoying him.

episodes.name: Spin the Bottle
episodes.overview: Plankton poses as a wish-granting genie in his latest scheme to get the secret formula.

episodes.name: Cave Dwelling Sponge
episodes.overview: When a prehistoric sponge is unfrozen, he causes chaos all over town and only SpongeBob can communicate with him.

episodes.name: The Clam Whisperer
episodes.overview: When a flock of clams descend on Bikini Bottom, SpongeBob has to get them out before they ruin the whole town.

episodes.name: Man Ray Returns
episodes.overview: When Man Ray rents Squidward's house for the weekend, it's up to SpongeBob and Patrick to stop his evil vacation.

episodes.name: Larry the Floor Manager
episodes.overview: Mr. Krabs takes a vacation and makes Larry the Lobster the temporary manager of the Krusty Krab.

episodes.name: Feral Friends
episodes.overview: A weird moon turns everyone in the city into wild animals, and Sandy is the only one who can save them.

episodes.name: Don't Wake Patrick
episodes.overview: Patrick sleepwalks and SpongeBob can't wake him up.

episodes.name: The Legend of Boo-Kini Bottom
episodes.overview: The Flying Dutchman wants to make sure SpongeBob and his friends are scared on Halloween.

episodes.name: Krabby Patty Creature Feature
episodes.overview: A new secret Krabby Patty formula has disastrous results for Bikini Bottom, and only SpongeBob can save the day.

episodes.name: Teacher's Pests
episodes.overview: Mr. Krabs and Plankton have to take boating school classes.

episodes.name: No Pictures, Please
episodes.overview: Patrick leads an enthusiastic stranger on a tour of his favorite places in Bikini Bottom.

episodes.name: Stuck on the Roof
episodes.overview: SpongeBob is afraid to get off the roof of the Krusty Krab, but he won't let that stop him from living his life!

episodes.name: There's a Sponge in My Soup
episodes.overview: Mr. Krabs’ new Krabby soup is a hit – until some heat-loving hippies move into the soup vat!

episodes.name: Cuddle E. Hugs
episodes.overview: SpongeBob's new friend is a giant, fluffy hamster, but no one else is able to see him.

episodes.name: ScavengerPants
